# Keep the Docker build context small and the image clean.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/.next
**/.vite
**/coverage

# Web + desktop apps are not part of the server image.
apps/web/dist
apps/desktop/dist
apps/desktop/dist-electron
apps/desktop/release

# VCS / editor / OS noise
.git
.gitignore
.github
**/.DS_Store
**/*.log

# Local env + secrets (never bake into the image, at any depth)
**/.env
**/.env.*
!.env.example

# Docs / scratch
*.md
!README.md
